---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About"
	description="Hi, I'm Batota — programming, IT, and a legendary traveler."
	pubDate={new Date('August 08 2021')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p>Hi, I'm Batota.</p>
	<p>
		The name is a mix of IT/programming and Batota, inspired by a legendary traveler.
		I don't travel the world — I travel through codebases, legacy projects, and unexpected errors.
	</p>
	<p>This site exists to share:</p>
	<ul>
		<li>things I learned the hard way</li>
		<li>explanations without pretending to be a genius</li>
		<li>real tech, real mistakes, real fixes</li>
	</ul>
	<p>
		No motivational speeches.<br />
		Just lessons earned by debugging.
	</p>
</Layout>
